{"title":"送暖信——寄给中国人民志愿军","authors":["谷峪"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":1,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"送暖信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——寄给中国人民志愿军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷峪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿了，我想起你们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷了，我想起你们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的消息使我振奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要用我的心来温暖你们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雪下了五天整，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门窗结冰墨水冻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起了前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满屋子热腾腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起了你们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墨笔在我手里开了冻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们盖着雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们睡着冰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你们想到祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们心中燃起了一把火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰雪在你们身上融化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严寒在你们面前发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无耻的敌人跪下来哀求。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的同志呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我捎上我的信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我捎上我的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用我的信来暖你的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用我的心来暖你的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一、一、八"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}